Revision history for Text-Tabs

2013.0523 Thu 23 May 2013
 - Packaging fix

2013.0522 Wed 22 May 2013
 - No functional changes
 - Documentation typo fixes

2013.0426 Fri 26 Apr 2013
 - License change to qualify as "open source"
 [FIXES]
 - Another "this shouldn't happen" [cpan #79766]

2012.0818 Sat 18 Aug 2012
 - Packaging fix

2012.0815 Wed 15 Aug 2012
 - Bifurcated codebase for support of older perls
 [INCOMPATIBLE CHANGE]
 - Unicode support for perls that have \X

2009.0305 Thu 05 Mar 2009
 - Automatic increment of $columns when unavoidable

2006.1117 Fri 17 Nov 2006
 - Switch Text::Wrap from warn to warnings::warnif

2006.0711 Tue 11 Jul 2006
 [FIXES]
 - Another "this shouldn't happen"

2006.0705 Wed 05 Jul 2006
 [FIXES]
 - Wrapping long words under $break [perl #34902]
 - Wrapping under $columns=1

2005.0824 Wed 24 Aug 2005
 - Separate line ending configuration for computed linebreaks
 [FIXES]
 - Wrapping long words [perl #17141]

2001.0929 Sat 29 Sep 2001
 - Retention of tainting on input strings in output string
 - Configurable line ending in Text::Wrap
 [INCOMPATIBLE CHANGE]
 - No automatic unexpand of Text::Wrap output

2001.0131 Tue 30 Jan 2001
 - New setting for $huge to split overlong words
 [FIXES]
 - No extraneous whitespace when passed multiple strings

98.112902 Sun 29 Nov 1998
 - Merge of Text::Fill into Text::Wrap

98.112801 Sat 28 Nov 1998
 - New configuration variable $huge in Text::Wrap
 - New module Text::Fill

97.011701 Fri 17 Jan 1997
 [INCOMPATIBLE CHANGE]
 - Overflow when wrapping overlong words is now silent

96.121201 Thu 12 Dec 1996
 [FIXES]
 - @l[0] --> $l[0]

96.090101 Sun 01 Sep 1996
 - Removal of Text::Wrap::fill

96.082801 Wed 28 Aug 1996
 - New Text::Wrap::fill for wrapping multiple paragraphs

96.051501 Wed 15 May 1996
 [FIXES]
 - No loss of trailing empty lines in unexpand

96.050901 Thu 09 May 1996
 - Initial release
